      "name": "酒館挑戰",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "友好對局·魔偶劍鬼的緣起",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "關卡介紹",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「喵...」「是很久很久以前，從一隻躲在稻妻船裡的貓告訴我的...說在稻妻，有這樣一種機關劍鬼...」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "【特殊規則】「魔偶劍鬼」免疫凍結、眩暈、石化，初始裝備有天賦牌「機巧神通」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "對手陣容",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3355,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/17/84496276/e094091fc58ea928dba3da71fca7ff5a_5885816954298421011.png",
